snippet.title: "Thank You" -  Johnny Depp Thanks Fans For Defending Him Against Amber Heard...
snippet.description:
"Thank You" -  Johnny Depp Thanks Fans For Defending Him Against Amber Heard...
One of the most interesting things to come from the Johnny Depp case that is going on right now is his support system. Because his ex-wife in Amber Heard has been going and proclaiming for years that Johnny Depp has been to her during their time together (which included years of dating and a 1-year marriage for the record). But yet, there have been many, MANY people in the celeb world, his personal life, and the fans who have not believed this since day one. And recently, Depp decided to go and thank those who have supported him. We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the current state of the Johnny Depp situation and how he's grateful to those who have supported him throughout it. Do you think that Johnny knows that without this support he might not have made it through these last five years of court battles? Do you think the fans and celeb support will continue to build up until he's exonerated? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
